snippet.title: FILM TIME
snippet.description:
FILM TIME is a channel dedicated to giving you the story recaps of movies. 
Giving you a general idea of a movie which then, if you wish to, you can fully watch the movie.
Let's enjoy the movies!

Subscribe for more movies:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmJHp21CdwdvYAcUekTHRHg
